Text: Ercot Load appletApplication Cc on the ercot load appletapplication is located on the file server M Drive rather than running locally from the client PC There are ways to run the appletapplication As desktop application Create an Desktop ShortCut which points to the following file MFundamental AnalysisDevelopmentErcotsercotjar Or simply COPY the Ercot RT Load shortcut under MFundamental AnalysisDevelopmentErcot and PASTE it to your desktop As browser applets ercothtml if you never visit the site before you need to setup security certification call me x and I can install it for you Let me know if anyone have any problems Thanks aw From Kayne Coulter ECT PM To Alex nron cc Subject Ercot Load Rudy Acevedo Juan Hernandez Kayne Coulter Mitch Robinson These are the names that you asked for Thanks Kayne
